</taxonomicName>
, ♀. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[768,789,1902,1928]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">A</emphasis>
. Lateral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[962,982,1902,1928]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">B</emphasis>
