<paragraph blockId="6.[189,1315,1773,1799]" box="[189,1315,1773,1799]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">The species is only known from the Knersvlakte, a semi-desert plane in southern Namaqualand.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[189,337,1839,1865]" box="[189,337,1839,1865]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,337,1839,1865]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" reason="3">
